---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Refund Policy — AccelliTec"
  description="AccelliTec's refund policy for webinars, training cohorts, and consulting engagements. Clear timelines and conditions."
  canonical="/refund"
>
  <Nav />

  <div class="legal-wrap">
    <div class="page-label">Legal</div>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:2.8rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:12px;">Refund Policy</h1>
    <div class="last-updated">Last updated: March 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Effective immediately</div>

    <div class="intro-box">
      At AccelliTec, we are committed to delivering high-quality training and consulting experiences. We understand that circumstances change, and this policy outlines clearly when and how refunds are applicable.
    </div>

    <div class="summary-grid">
      <div class="summary-card green">
        <span class="summary-icon">✅</span>
        <div class="summary-title">Full Refund</div>
        <div class="summary-desc">Cancellation 7+ days before session or AccelliTec cancels</div>
      </div>
      <div class="summary-card gold">
        <span class="summary-icon">⚡</span>
        <div class="summary-title">Partial Refund</div>
        <div class="summary-desc">Cancellation 3–6 days before session starts</div>
      </div>
      <div class="summary-card red">
        <span class="summary-icon">❌</span>
        <div class="summary-title">No Refund</div>
        <div class="summary-desc">Less than 48 hours before session or after session starts</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2><span class="num">01</span> Webinars & Masterclasses</h2>
      <div class="policy-box eligible">
        <div class="policy-box-title">✅ Full Refund Eligible</div>
        <ul>
          <li>You request a refund 7 or more days before the scheduled session date</li>
          <li>AccelliTec cancels or postpones the session and you do not wish to attend the rescheduled date</li>
          <li>Technical failure on AccelliTec's end prevents the session from taking place</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-box partial">
        <div class="policy-box-title">⚡ 50% Refund</div>
        <ul>
          <li>You request a refund 3 to 6 days before the scheduled session date</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-box not-eligible">
        <div class="policy-box-title">❌ No Refund</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Cancellation requested less than 48 hours before the session</li>
          <li>You do not attend the session (no-show)</li>
          <li>Session recording has already been shared with you</li>
          <li>You have already attended part of the session</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="divider"/>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2><span class="num">02</span> Training Cohorts & Bootcamps</h2>
      <div class="policy-box eligible">
        <div class="policy-box-title">✅ Full Refund Eligible</div>
        <ul>
          <li>You request a refund before the cohort officially starts (before Week 1 Session 1)</li>
          <li>AccelliTec cancels the cohort entirely</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-box partial">
        <div class="policy-box-title">⚡ Partial Refund (Pro-rated)</div>
        <ul>
          <li>You withdraw after Week 1 but before Week 3 — 50% refund of remaining weeks</li>
          <li>Circumstances beyond your control (medical emergency with documentation) — case by case basis</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-box not-eligible">
        <div class="policy-box-title">❌ No Refund</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Withdrawal after Week 3 of any cohort</li>
          <li>Dissatisfaction with content after attending 3 or more sessions</li>
          <li>Failure to attend sessions without prior notice</li>
          <li>Inability to complete the course due to personal schedule changes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <p>We strongly recommend attending the <strong>free webinar</strong> before enrolling in any paid cohort to ensure the content meets your expectations.</p>
    </div>
    <hr class="divider"/>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2><span class="num">03</span> Consulting Engagements</h2>
      <p>Consulting projects are governed by a separate Statement of Work (SOW) or consulting agreement. Refund terms for consulting services will be explicitly defined in the signed agreement for each engagement.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Discovery calls and initial consultations are free — no payment, no refund applicable</li>
        <li>Retainer fees paid in advance are non-refundable once work has commenced</li>
        <li>Project milestone payments are non-refundable once the milestone is delivered and accepted</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <hr class="divider"/>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2><span class="num">04</span> How to Request a Refund</h2>
      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">STEP 1</span>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Email us at info@accellitec.com</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Subject line: "Refund Request — [Your Name] — [Service Name]". Include your registered email, payment reference number, and reason for refund.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">STEP 2</span>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">We review your request within 2 business days</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Our team will verify your purchase and confirm refund eligibility based on this policy.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">STEP 3</span>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Refund processed within 7 business days</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Approved refunds are returned to the original payment method. UPI/bank transfers may take 5–7 business days to reflect in your account.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="divider"/>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2><span class="num">05</span> Transfers & Substitutions</h2>
      <p>Instead of a refund, you may request:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Session transfer</strong> — move your registration to the next available batch (subject to availability)</li>
        <li><strong>Credit transfer</strong> — your payment credited toward any other AccelliTec service of equal or higher value</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Transfer requests must be made at least 48 hours before the session starts.</p>
    </div>
    <hr class="divider"/>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2><span class="num">06</span> Exceptional Circumstances</h2>
      <p>AccelliTec evaluates refund requests arising from genuine emergencies (medical, bereavement, natural disaster) on a case-by-case basis, regardless of the standard policy timeline. Please email us with supporting documentation and we will do our best to accommodate you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-box">
      <h3>Have a refund question?</h3>
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@accellitec.com">info@accellitec.com</a></p>
      <p>We respond within 24–48 hours on business days (Monday to Friday, IST).</p>
      <p style="margin-top:12px;font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--muted);">We always aim to resolve concerns fairly. If you're unsatisfied with a service, please reach out before requesting a refund — we'll do everything we can to make it right.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);text-align:center;padding:24px;position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <a href="/" style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;margin:0 12px;">← Home</a>
    <a href="/terms" style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;margin:0 12px;">Terms & Conditions</a>
    <a href="mailto:info@accellitec.com" style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;margin:0 12px;">info@accellitec.com</a>
  </footer>
</Layout>
